       +----------------------+
       |   Mobile App         |
       | (User's Device)      |
       +----------------------+
                |
                |  Scans QR code & sends authentication request
                v
       +---------------------------+
       | Central Server/Backend    |
       | (Authentication, validation, log) |
       +---------------------------+
                |    ^
                |    | Generates dynamic QR code update
                v    |
       +---------------------------+
       | Embedded Device           |
       | (E-Paper Display)         |
       +---------------------------+
                |
                | Receives unlock command and triggers door action
                v
       +---------------------+
       | Door Lock Mechanism |
       +---------------------+
                |
                | Logs access events
                v
       +-------------------------+
       | Access Log Database     |
       +-------------------------+

